Food Products

Company Overview of Smithfield Foods, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Smithfield Foods, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, produces and markets various fresh meat and packaged meats products in the United States and internationally. It operates through five segments: Fresh Pork, Packaged Meats, Hog Production, International, and Corporate. The company offers fresh pork products, such as butts, loins, picnics, and ribs, as well as leaners; hogs; and beef and poultry products. It also produces packaged meats, including smoked and boiled hams, bacon, sausage, hot dogs, deli, canned meats, and luncheon meats; specialty products comprising pepperoni, dry meat products, and ready-to-eat products; and prepared foods consisting of pre-cooked entrees and bacon. The ...
Smithfield Foods, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, produces and markets various fresh meat and packaged meats products in the United States and internationally. It operates through five segments: Fresh Pork, Packaged Meats, Hog Production, International, and Corporate. The company offers fresh pork products, such as butts, loins, picnics, and ribs, as well as leaners; hogs; and beef and poultry products. It also produces packaged meats, including smoked and boiled hams, bacon, sausage, hot dogs, deli, canned meats, and luncheon meats; specialty products comprising pepperoni, dry meat products, and ready-to-eat products; and prepared foods consisting of pre-cooked entrees and bacon. The company markets its products to supermarket chains; wholesale distributors; the foodservice industry, including fast food, restaurant and hotel chains, hospitals, and other institutional customers; export markets; and other further processors. Smithfield Foods sells its products through salespersons and independent commission brokers. The company was founded in 1936 and is headquartered in Smithfield, Virginia. As of September 26, 2013, Smithfield Foods, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Henan Luohe Shuanghui Industry Group Limited Liability Company.

