Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Staples
Industry: Consumer Products
Sub-Industry: Agricultural Producers
Smithfield Foods, Inc. provides food products. The Company offers frozen barbecues and chilies, peanuts, and pork products. Smithfield Foods operates in the United States.




